What is Array: Array is a collection of similar data type
Ex:  Array  of integer,Array of String, Array of char, array of double ..etc

How to create Arrays:
Single dimension Array Synatx:
datatype arrayname[] = new datatype[size];
int arr[] = new int[3];
arr[0] = 0;
arr[1] = 1;
arr[2] = 2;
*Limitation of arrays :
		 * Cannot change the size dynamically , its fixed
		 * Cannot change the array type once defined

How to retrieve value from array.
2 D array